    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable budget option for those who prioritize function over aesthetics. While the engine and transmission are operational, the car shows noticeable signs of age, including some interior wear and minor exterior blemishes. It has been regularly serviced, though it will eventually require some cosmetic attention and minor repairs to bring it back to its best. It is a solid, honest car for anyone needing dependable transportation at a reasonable price.",
