      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This 987.1 Cayman S features the 3.4L flat-six M97 powerplant, delivering linear torque through a precise 6-speed manual transaxle. The mid-engine architecture provides an exceptional polar moment of inertia, complemented by PASM-equipped dampers and a stiffened chassis. Recent maintenance includes a full cooling system refresh and a Blackstone oil analysis confirming no bore scoring. The hydraulic steering rack remains communicative and leak-free. While the exterior shows honest road wear, the mechanical synchronization of the drivetrain remains tight, with the Sport Chrono package sharpening throttle mapping for peak heel-and-toe engagement.",
